  "title": "A graphical assessment of data from intercropping factorial experiments",
  "abstract": "A graphical method, based on bivariate analysis, is used to present yield data from intercropping experiments involving two crop species. The method is used to demonstrate two- and three-factor interactions in factorial experiments",
